{
  "stem": "18932.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 368.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stood there for a little while, and then they decided they have to concentrate people in-- in smaller places because they need more room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put me and my mother into another-- couple with a daughter, in their apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they gave us a bed on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they hated us, like it was our fault that they put us into their houses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it really, you know, was not our fault.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't want to leave our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- this was really the Jewish government on the instruction of the Germans, because they told them what to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a government.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was policemen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- there was, you know, a whole body.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, the president was Rumkowski, and he has a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, my father worked for them, too, before they caught him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And no matter what he said, they just-- you couldn't talk to anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just put you in a truck and just evacuated you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were the people that were issuing all kinds of rules that we had to obey, even though the-- it was just the German that told the Jews what to do.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had to go to the other people's apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really can't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a daughter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were very mean to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us-- our bed on the place where there was-- the water was coming down when it rains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once my mother and me had to sleep with an umbrella, holding the umbrella up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was really very tough times.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
